OL,7,FScotland's first minister and justice
OL,8,Fsecretary have been under continued
OL,9,Fpressure to launch a public inquiry
OL,10,Finto group-based sexual abuse, similar
OL,11,Fto the grooming inquiry ongoing in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FThe government has said it "remains
OL,15,Fopen" but that there is not enough
OL,16,Fevidence to justify such an inquiry in
OL,17,FScotland.
