OL,7,FTaylor grew up in the care system and
OL,8,Fit's here she said she was picked up
OL,9,Fregularly by a group of Pakistani men
OL,10,Fand driven to flats in Glasgow where
OL,11,Fshe and her friend were sexually
OL,12,Fabused.
OL,14,FShe says this started when she was 13
OL,15,Fand lasted for at least four years
OL,16,Funtil she finally put a stop to it
OL,17,Fherself.
