OL,7,F"A few times, I woke up when I had
OL,8,Fonly been drinking alcohol out of a
OL,9,Fbottle, but I had no recollection of
OL,10,Fthe night before. I was lying on a
OL,11,Fdirty mattress on the floor, naked,
OL,12,Fwith a cover over me.
OL,14,F"Other times I do remember, you would
OL,15,Fsleep with them because they would
OL,16,Fsay, 'we've been good to you, we've
OL,17,Fpicked you up, we gave you this, we
OL,18,Fgave you that'. At times, it felt like
OL,19,FI had to."
