OL,7,FBut she recently opened her care files
OL,8,Ffor the first time and was shocked to
OL,9,Flearn that in 2013, police had visited
OL,10,Fher care unit as part of an inquiry
OL,11,Finto potential grooming gangs.
OL,13,FThe files note that officers said
OL,14,FTaylor had been put on a list which
OL,15,Fidentified her "along with 45 other
OL,16,Fyoung people as... being vulnerable to
OL,17,Fsexual exploitation."
