OL,8,Fthat police and social work were aware
OL,9,Fshe was a potential victim, but that
OL,10,Fnobody told her or attempted to make
OL,11,Fit stop.
OL,13,F"Nobody spoke to me about that, not
OL,14,Fone member of staff, no police
OL,15,Fofficer. My mum wasn't informed about
OL,16,Fthat visit from the police. Not once
OL,17,Fwas it mentioned."
