OL,7,FA spokesperson for Police Scotland
OL,8,Fsays: "We take a multi-agency approach
OL,9,Fwhen dealing with child sexual
OL,10,Fexploitation. Information is shared
OL,11,Fbetween partners, but this would not
OL,12,Fnecessarily instigate an immediate
OL,13,Finvestigation, as we would require the
OL,14,Fexpress consent of the potential
OL,15,Fvictim before proceeding. We would
